text: Antun Kropivšek (17 May 1925 - 12 July 2013) was a Croatian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Croatian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Šentjur
